Set Profile as active and reset it 

Precondition:
Create TS Project.
Create profile for testing. 

Test steps:
Reset profile
Check active profile in Tigerstripe/Active Profile Details...
Set testing profile as active profile.
Check active profile in Tigerstripe/Active Profile Details...
Check Profile name, version and description.
Reset profile.

